    {
      "id": "de7fcead-23b7-450d-a806-f07d9f4b2d55",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper starts with a discussion of the potential of Learning Analytics for the early identification of students at risk. However there are important challenges that warrant addressing with Data imbalance being among the most important ones.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "de7fcead-23b7-450d-a806-f07d9f4b2d55",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
